Rafferty('s) rules
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:espec.(BE) RUN ON RAFFERTY RULES, of a game, a household, a raffle, etc, (be run) without a sense of order, method, correctness, etc; with no rules at all


